^RThe Rules
^NThe object is for people to mix with each other and enjoy themselves.
With that in mind there are a few simple rules designed to make life
better for everyone.

        ^R*^N No swearing. We do not allow swearing of any sort.
        ^R*^N Nothing offensive. This includes harrassment.
        ^R*^N Nothing illegal. This includes drugs and pirate software.
        ^R*^N No multiple characters.
        ^R*^N No spamming.
        ^R*^N No advertising other talkers or muds.
        ^R*^N No public talking in a language other than English.
        ^R*^N The word of the Staff is final.

A more detailed description can be found in 'help rules' when you get into the
program.

